text:
Taught my kids the 9x trick for single digits & their minds are BLOWN!!! lol
9*A=(A - 1) & (9 - (A - 1))
9x1 = (1 - 1) and (9 - (1 - 1)) = 0 & 9 = 9
9x2 = (2 - 1) and (9 - (2 - 1)) = 1 & 8 = 18
9x3 = (3 - 1) and (9 - (3 - 1)) = 2 & 7 = 27
etc...
